Everything about my visit to Cafe Monarch was exceptional.
First, we were immediately intrigued by the brightly colored wall paint that had the two brunch choices for the day.
Sweet & Savory.
Both options sounded great, but I went for the Savory - which was a grilled salmon with tomato sauce & a baked spinach & potato quiche.
